casebody.data:
OKLAHOMA, et al., petitioners,
v.
ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION AGENCY, et al. No. 13-921. Supreme Court of the United States May 27, 2014. Case below, 723 F.3d 1201 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
